---
// src/components/Testimonios.astro
// Sección de testimonios / casos de éxito
---

<section class="testimonios-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <span class="section-badge">Casos de éxito</span>
      <h2>Lo que dicen nuestros clientes</h2>
      <p>Joyerías reales con resultados reales</p>
    </div>

    <div class="testimonios-grid">
      <!-- Testimonio 1 -->
      <article class="testimonio-card">
        <div class="testimonio-quote">
          <svg class="quote-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
            <path d="M6 17h3l2-4V7H5v6h3zm8 0h3l2-4V7h-6v6h3z"/>
          </svg>
          <p>"Probamos 3 ERPs genéricos antes de RayGold. Ninguno entendía que una alianza tiene oro de 18k, un diamante de 0.15ct y mano de obra de grabado. <strong>RayGold lo trae de serie.</strong>"</p>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonio-result">
          <span class="result-number">-60%</span>
          <span class="result-text">tiempo de inventario</span>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonio-author">
          <div class="author-avatar">CN</div>
          <div class="author-info">
            <strong>Carlos Navarro</strong>
            <span>Joyería Navarro e Hijos · Valencia</span>
            <span class="author-years">Cliente desde 2012</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- Testimonio 2 -->
      <article class="testimonio-card featured">
        <div class="testimonio-quote">
          <svg class="quote-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
            <path d="M6 17h3l2-4V7H5v6h3zm8 0h3l2-4V7h-6v6h3z"/>
          </svg>
          <p>"Gestionamos 4.000 referencias con variantes de oro, plata y aleaciones. Las órdenes de fabricación de RayGold calculan el metal exacto. <strong>Antes lo hacíamos en Excel.</strong>"</p>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonio-result">
          <span class="result-number">12.000€</span>
          <span class="result-text">ahorro anual en mermas</span>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonio-author">
          <div class="author-avatar">MO</div>
          <div class="author-info">
            <strong>María José Ordaz</strong>
            <span>Fabricaciones Ordaz · Córdoba</span>
            <span class="author-years">Cliente desde 2016</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- Testimonio 3 -->
      <article class="testimonio-card">
        <div class="testimonio-quote">
          <svg class="quote-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
            <path d="M6 17h3l2-4V7H5v6h3zm8 0h3l2-4V7h-6v6h3z"/>
          </svg>
          <p>"Abrimos la quinta tienda y RayGold escaló sin problemas. Stock centralizado, traspasos entre tiendas, comisiones... <strong>Es nuestro cerebro operativo.</strong>"</p>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonio-result">
          <span class="result-number">5</span>
          <span class="result-text">tiendas sincronizadas</span>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonio-author">
          <div class="author-avatar">JP</div>
          <div class="author-info">
            <strong>Jordi Puig</strong>
            <span>Grupo Brillante · Cataluña</span>
            <span class="author-years">Cliente desde 2009</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .testimonios-section {
    padding: 5rem 1.5rem;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #0f172a 0%, #1e293b 100%);
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .section-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    background: rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.2);
    color: #818cf8;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    border-radius: 50px;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .section-header h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: white;
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
  }

  .section-header p {
    color: #94a3b8;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .testimonios-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(340px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .testimonio-card {
    background: rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.6);
    border: 1px solid #334155;
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 1.75rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .testimonio-card:hover {
    border-color: #667eea;
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
  }

  .testimonio-card.featured {
    border-color: #667eea;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.15) 0%, rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.6) 100%);
  }

  .testimonio-quote {
    position: relative;
  }

  .quote-icon {
    width: 32px;
    height: 32px;
    color: #667eea;
    opacity: 0.5;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .testimonio-quote p {
    color: #e2e8f0;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .testimonio-quote strong {
    color: white;
  }

  .testimonio-result {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    padding: 1rem;
    background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.3);
    border-radius: 10px;
  }

  .result-number {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #10b981;
  }

  .result-text {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: #94a3b8;
  }

  .testimonio-author {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding-top: 1rem;
    border-top: 1px solid #334155;
  }

  .author-avatar {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea, #764ba2);
    border-radius: 12px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: white;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .author-info {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.125rem;
  }

  .author-info strong {
    color: white;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .author-info span {
    color: #94a3b8;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
  }

  .author-years {
    color: #667eea !important;
    font-size: 0.75rem !important;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .testimonios-section {
      padding: 3rem 1rem;
    }

    .section-header h2 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }

    .testimonios-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
